 	<div id="main-article-info">

		
		
			<h1 itemprop="name headline  "
								>The Odyssey: a soldier's road home</h1>
		
					<div itemprop="description" id="stand-first"
				 class="stand-first-alone"                        	        data-component="Article:standfirst_cta"			>After the Trojan war, Odysseus sets off on his journey back to Ithaca. He survives encounters with the Lotus Eaters and Sirens only to face another challenge: the homecoming. What can Homer's epic poem tell us about how soldiers cope when conflicts end?</div>
		
		
  	</div>

  	  	    			<ul id="content-actions" class="share-links trackable-component"         	        data-component="Article:top share tools">
				                
    
	
		
												


    
    
    	
    	
    	

